description: The folks of San Jose shout a loud “Yay!” whenever they spot Sodacraft, Mark & Sara’s special spunky truck. Here, you can find their homemade craft sodas that are as bubbly as their personalities, as well as fun popcorn and pretzels that are as fantastically warm and delightful as they are! These two know how to make soda so yum, and they manage to do it with completely natural, organic, and local ingredients. Come try out their classics like Cola, Blood Orange, and Lemon Lime Twist, as well as their seasonal selection. It’s truly the best fizz in the biz!
name: Sodacraft
